data.description:
Discover your own piece of paradise on this sprawling 26.2-acre (MOL) estate, featuring not one, but two homes, two picturesque ponds, and two spacious shops with above ground swimming pool! The primary custom-built residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a secondary living room, and an office space, offering room to roam and endless possibilities. Revel in the beauty of nature as you soak in sunrise and sunset views from your covered back patio, the inviting dock house, or the charming fishing dock overlooking a stunning pond. This property is a rare gem, combining serenity, space, and convenience for your dream lifestyle. 

Adjacent to the second home, a versatile garage/shop provides more functionality. Complete with a full kitchen featuring custom-built wooden cabinets, a bathroom, and a cozy wood-burning stove, this space is a fantastic addition to the property, perfect for a multitude of purposes.
Nestled outside city limits, this property is a haven for wildlife enthusiasts. Witness deer, wild turkeys, and the annual migration of geese, a nature lover's delight right in your backyard. The location of this country oasis keeps you near major highways, a community hospital, with advanced education programs (USAO & Canadian Valley Tech.), and PLENTY of food, retail, & entertainment. “more photos upon request”
